  <thing id="cEXMSklArt" name="Skill Artistry 1" description="An exemplar is particularly talented in the use of one of her skills. choose one skill in which the exemplar has at least 13 ranks. she gains a +4 competence bonus on all checks involving that skill.\nAt 4th, 7th, and 10th levels, an exemplar gains this ability again, each time she selects a different skill to recieve the bonus, if no skill meets the 13 ranks requirement, the ability confers no benefit until the exemplar has 13 ranks in another skill." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Gain +4 to a proficient skill (13 ranks)">
