  <thing id="cEXMSusPrs" name="Sustaining Presence" description="Starting at 4th level, an exemplar knows how to call upon her force of personality to help keep herself alive in tense or dangerous situations. she adds her charisma bonus (if any) to her concentration checks and fortitude saves." compset="ClSpecial" summary="add Charisma to Fort and Concentration">
