  <thing id="cEMPIntAgi" name="Intellectual Agility" description="Starting at 8th Ievel, an exemplar can channel her intellect to more physical needs. She adds her intelligence bonus (if any) to her intiative checks and Reflex saves." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Add Int to initiative and reflex">
