  <thing id="cMMFEveFor" name="Evershifting Form" description="A 10th-level master of many forms has reached the pinnacle of her shapechanging abilities. She gains the shapechanger subtype and becomes immune to any transmutation effect unless she is willing to accept it.\n\nIn addition, she no longer takes ability penalties for aging and is not subject to magical aging, though any aging penalties she already may have taken remain in place. Bonuses still accrue, and a master of many forms still dies of old age when her time is up." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Gain shapechanger subtype and imm to transmute unless willing, no age pen.">
