  <thing id="wShoSwdBr" name="Shortsword, Broadblade" description="If you are proficient with the broadblade short sword and you fight defensively or employ the total defense combat maneuver, you gain an additional +2 dodge bonus to your AC on top of the normal bonus. This bonus also applies if you are proficient, have the Combat Expertise feat, and shift at least 2 points of your attack bonus to AC for the round.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Adventurer" compset="Weapon">
