  <thing id="wRapierQ" name="Rapier, Quickblade" description="If you are proficient with the quickblade rapier, you gain a +2 bonus on opposed attack rolls made to disarm an enemy (including the roll to avoid being disarmed if such an attempt fails). You also gain a +2 circumstance bonus on Bluff checks made to feint in combat.\n\nYou can use Weapon Finesse with a Quickblade Rapier, even though it isn&apos;t light. You can&apos;t wield it in both hands to get extra damage from your strength bonus.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Adventurer" compset="Weapon">
