  <thing id="cSctBaFor1" name="Battle Fortitude +1" description="At 2nd level, a scout gains a +1 competence bonus on Fortitude saves and initiative checks. This bonus increases to +2 at 11th level and +3 at 20th level. A scout loses this bonus when wearing medium or heavy armor or when carrying a medium or heavy load." compset="ClSpecial" summary="+1 bonus to Init and Fort saves when in Light armor and unencumbered">
